### Google Streets (layer spec)

| Field | Value |
|-------|-------|
| name | Google Streets |
| source | road infrastructure, building footprints, labels |
| tier | 1 |
| update_frequency | weekly (on WiFi) |
| offline | cached within 2-mile corridor |
| ui_label | STREETS |
| features | roads, buildings, place names, addresses |

### Layer switching logic

- **Default:** TOPO + STREETS (Tier 1, always available).
- **On connectivity:** Hybrid 4.0 loads as overlay.
- **User control:** Layer toggle buttons (radio or segmented control).

### 2-mile mission corridor (refined)

- Pre-cache **all** Tier 1 layers within 2-mile radius of active path.
- Hybrid 4.0 caches opportunistically (when bandwidth permits).
- Cache invalidation: **7-day TTL** or manual clear.

### Implementation constraints

- Vector Topography **must** work offline (no fallback to online tiles for this layer).
- Layer switching **must not** reload the entire map (visibility toggle only).
- Hybrid 4.0 **must** show loading state plus offline badge when unavailable (copy: **⚠️ Last cached** per layer spec above).



